```r
sinspuPCoAMeta %>%
  left_join(.,sinspuk4) %>%
  rename(cluster = sinspuk4) -> sinspuPCoAMeta

sinspuPCoAMeta %>%
  group_by(cluster) %>%
  summarise(cluster.Dim1 = mean(Dim1),
            cluster.Dim2 = mean(Dim2)) -> clusterCentroid

ggplot(sinspuPCoAMeta,
       aes(x = Dim1,
           y = Dim2,
           color = factor(cluster))) +
  geom_point(size = 2,
             alpha = 0.5) +
  scale_color_manual(name = \Cluster\"
